\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 YOu little brat! Don\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t you know I just killed your father?}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Look at the poor thing. Can\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t be older than four. She\u8217\'92s no idea what\u8217\'92s going on. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Pyetle kicked her off him.}
